Happy Caturday from Benny! Born mid-May, 2017, Benny is a lively boy who wants to play all day every day. His Foster Mom's home flooded during Hurricane Harvey, but they got Benny and his friends out before there was any danger. Benny is glad that he has such a smart Foster Mom! So now Benny is vacationing at a local pet spa while his foster mom figures out what to do with her house. He and some other fosters cats are roommates and are having such a good time. But even a kitten knows that vacations can't last forever and it is time to find his permanent home. 
If you are interested in Benny contact www.homelesspets.net
